{"tid":45202,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"下星期去韓國 著幾多件衫先夠做 [bomb]","createTime":"2016-12-18T20:23:20.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-26T23:09:02.000Z","uid":29632,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c1caf234f8eb225695c755f97fab722cc4c97ece","tid":45202,"uid":29632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T20:23:20.000Z","msg":"屎忽痕未睇過雪 見到有平機票就狗衝左 但又唔記得自己唔襟凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想問有冇巴絲近排去可以分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a8eb8b486cb4dd11a4b8834c95f16a1ab6a2cd7","tid":45202,"uid":18741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T20:28:12.000Z","msg":"李彩華.jpg"},{"pid":"d3fc47e60feb163c64c4dfa6041c4052da754a02","tid":45202,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T20:39:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://vignette3.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/f/f7/%E6%9D%8E%E5%BD%A9%E8%8F%AF%E5%B0%8F%E8%83%8C%E5%BF%83.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20070228115250\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvignette3.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Ff%2Ff7%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%25BD%25A9%25E8%258F%25AF%25E5%25B0%258F%25E8%2583%258C%25E5%25BF%2583.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20070228115250&h=e7f1f89d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"69229f5859bf9f3a11bdc03366bf2edd8297a99a","tid":45202,"uid":47849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T21:36:42.000Z","msg":"入面著薄啲，普通長袖衫<br />\n出面加件絨毛薄外套<br />\n再帶件厚羽絨<br />\n<br />\n因為韓國好多地方會有暖氣<br />\n例如巴士地鐵餐廳酒店<br />\n入面著太厚會超熱,又除唔到就大滯<br />\n<br />\n戶外會大風超凍,十二月尾打後都會落雪<br />\n所以要一件好保暖既外套<br />\n<br />\n日夜温差大<br />\n入夜6點真係會直跌當日預報最低温度<br />\n<br />\n所以要多層次,𡃴時可除可著<br />\n<br />\n上星期去完韓國，因為多戶外少室内<br />\n凍到變雪條<br />\n一般牛仔褲會太凍<br />\n入面要著保暖褲打底<br />\n<br />\n如果你係跟團多室內,<br />\n厚身牛仔褲應該冇問題"},{"pid":"c3d0b0852070926aaff79e1a7cdb78953f63b9e0","tid":45202,"uid":65530,"like":0,